  "texts": [
    "These models have demonstrated remarkable performance on metrics pertaining to helpfulness and safety, outperforming existing open-source counterparts and rivaling proprietary alternatives.",
    "Moreover, LLaMA 2 ensures safety through a range of measures, including safety-specific data annotation, redteaming exercises, and iterative assessments.",
    "The training process for LLaMA 2 adopts a multi-stage methodology, starting with the pre-training of the model using an extensive array of publicly accessible datasets.",
    "This initial phase plays an essential role in instructing the model with a comprehensive understanding of linguistic patterns and structures.",
    "Subsequently, the model undergoes supervised fine-tuning tailored specifically to accommodate dialogue-oriented applications, thereby refining its responses and interactions with users."
  ]
